net.sf.sprockets.content

Class GooglePlacesLoader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Loader<D>
      • android.content.AsyncTaskLoader<Places.Response<T>>
        • net.sf.sprockets.content.GooglePlacesLoader<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the Response type of the Places method that will be called. For example, if you provide Request.NEARBY_SEARCH then the response type would be List<Place>, if Request.DETAILS then Place, and so on.

    public class GooglePlacesLoader<T>
extends AsyncTaskLoader<Places.Response<T>>
    Loader that sends requests to the Google Places API and provides the responses. See Places for the types of requests that can be sent and the available parameters and returned fields for each one. If there is a problem communicating with the Google Places API service, null will be returned.
